inner revolution
=======================================
Revolution always occur when there is a explosion happen in our feeling.
All most all our business rotate around to manage the life but at certain point our emotional energy is gather
and unable to transfer in any direction then their is a healing in our feeling that break the boundary and
move in certain direction with high attention.

At the start of revolution human realize this is my life, I made for it, nothing is impossible,I can hear myself..etc
At this time they unable to explain but next step had been taken from inside for further movement.
There are much abstract energy has been created before the revolution and that energy only supply during hole journey of revolution.

***The energy of attention centralize on action during revolution***
***Either inner or outer revolution, it makes tremendous changes***

Inner revolution
-------------------------
Whatever action we perform that is one part but when we get hindrance in our own existence contentiously it might lead
for our revolution towards existence.
In other word you may feel yourself in different manor/ways that you can not explain.
You cannot get what happen to you instantly, you cannot say what happen to you.
you cant say how much I am suffering, you cant say what i am feeling...etc

This revolution arise in silence zone, the people around you can detect but a very little
because they are not under adventurous feeling but you are in every moment.

***Inner revolution changes your life for you only***

***Either inner or external revolution but it always comes from inside and it is in high potential by nature***

External revolution
-------------------------
If some one are not agree completely the arrangement around them ..like the arrangement of society/culture/country/management
/style of leaving/internment...etc.
It is obvious they fight(for solution) with self to do something for this arrangement, If the same process take long time it
centralize the energy and finally make them heal to break the boundary.

***External revolution stabilize people in new fashion***
***Nature is always in under revolution known as 'in being of streaming'***
